540.sl_source: Pri prsnem plavanju moški ne bi smeli nositi kopalk, ker omeji gibanje zadnjice.
540.en_source: When swimming breaststroke, men shouldn't wear swim shorts, as it really limits movement in the buttocks.
540.sl_trans: Moški pri prsnem plavanju ne bi smeli nositi plavalnih hlač, saj to zelo omejuje gibanje zadnjice.

541.en_source: But you knew that, didn't you?

542.en_source: I think your nose is bleeding.
542.sl_trans: Mislim, da vam teče kri iz nosu.

544.en_source: This happens to me all the time.
544.sl_trans: To se mi dogaja ves čas.

546.sl_source: Tudi jaz imam težave s krvavitvami iz nosu.
546.en_source: I have a nosebleed problem too.
546.sl_trans: Tudi jaz imam težave s krvavitvijo iz nosu.

551.sl_source: Nekaj te bom vprašal, pa želim, da odgovoriš iskreno.
551.en_source: I'm gonna ask you a question and I want you to answer me honestly.
551.sl_trans: Postavil vam bom vprašanje in želim, da mi iskreno odgovorite.

553.sl_source: Umreti zaradi mraza in lakote v gozdu, postati žival, ki bo hrana za neko večjo žival ali imeti občasne krvavitve iz nosu?
553.en_source: To die of cold and hunger in the woods, to become an animal that will be killed and eaten by some bigger animal or to have a nosebleed from time to time?
553.sl_trans: Umreti od mraza in lakote v gozdu, postati žival, ki jo bo ubila in pojedla kakšna večja žival, ali občasno krvaveti iz nosu?

554.sl_source: Postati žival, ki bo hrana za neko večjo žival.
554.en_source: To become an animal that will be killed and eaten by some bigger animal.
554.sl_trans: Postati žival, ki jo bo ubila in pojedla večja žival.

556.en_source: She doesn't suspect that you're lying?

557.sl_source: Zelo vesela sem, ker imamo nov par.
557.en_source: I'm very happy because we have a new couple.
557.sl_trans: Zelo sem vesel, ker imamo nov par.

558.sl_source: Poznata se le nekaj dni, a sta zaljubljena in povsem prikladna.
558.en_source: They met just two days ago but they're very much in love and perfectly suited.
558.sl_trans: Spoznala sta se šele pred dvema dnevoma, a sta zelo zaljubljena in se odlično ujemata.

559.sl_source: Oba imata enako težavo z nenadnimi krvavitvami iz nosu.
559.en_source: They both have the same problem with their noses, they bleed quite suddenly.
559.sl_trans: Oba imata enako težavo z nosom, ki nenadoma krvavi.

560.sl_source: Jutri bosta premeščena v dvoposteljno sobo z večjo garderobo in kopalnico.
560.en_source: Tomorrow they'll be transferred to a double room with a larger wardrobe and a larger bathroom.
560.sl_trans: Jutri ju bodo premestili v dvoposteljno sobo z večjo garderobo in večjo kopalnico.

561.sl_source: Tam bosta dva tedna, nadaljnja dva tedna pa bosta preživela na jahti.
561.en_source: They will remain in the double room for two weeks, and then they'll be transferred to the yachts for a further two weeks.
561.sl_trans: Dva tedna bodo bivali v dvoposteljni sobi, nato pa se bodo za nadaljnja dva tedna preselili na jahte.

562.sl_source: Želimo vama vso srečo in upamo, da se v mesto vrneta kot par.
562.en_source: We wish you every success and we hope you will return to the city as a couple.
562.sl_trans: Želimo vam veliko uspeha in upamo, da se boste v mesto vrnili kot par.

565.sl_source: Vajino razmerje bomo z osebjem strogo nadzorovali.
565.en_source: The course of your relationship will be monitored closely by our staff and by me personally.
565.sl_trans: Naše osebje in jaz osebno bosta skrbno spremljala potek vašega odnosa.

566.sl_source: Če naletita na kakršne koli težave, napetosti ali nasprotja, ki jih ne moreta rešiti sama, bosta dobila otroka.
566.en_source: If you encounter any problems, any tensions, any arguing, that you cannot resolve yourselves, you will be assigned children.
566.sl_trans: Če boste naleteli na težave, napetosti ali prepir, ki jih ne boste mogli rešiti sami, vam bodo dodeljeni otroci.

572.en_source: Well, I think you have quite dry hair.
572.sl_trans: Mislim, da imaš precej suhe lase.

574.en_source: The most important thing is that you're not bald.

575.sl_source: Je pa pri moških vedno tveganje, ki se mu težko ogneš.
575.en_source: However, when it comes to men, baldness is always a possibility you can't avoid.
575.sl_trans: Pri moških pa je plešavost vedno možnost, ki se ji ne morete izogniti.

578.sl_source: Pa četudi nekega dne izgubim lase, lahko to rešim.
578.en_source: And even if someday I lose my hair, there are things I can do to get my hair back.
578.sl_trans: Tudi če nekega dne izgubim lase, lahko storim marsikaj, da jih dobim nazaj.

579.en_source: I can have a hair transplant.

580.en_source: You can always tell when someone's had a hair transplant.
580.sl_trans: Vedno lahko opaziš, da je nekdo imel presaditev las.

581.sl_source: Lepi lasje niso nekaj, kar dobiš.
581.en_source: Nice hair is not something you can get.
581.sl_trans: Lepi lasje niso nekaj, kar bi lahko dobili.

582.sl_trans: To je nekaj, s čimer se rodite.

583.sl_source: Dejstvo, da tvoj oče ni plešast, tebe ne bi smelo pomirjati.
583.en_source: And the fact that your father isn't bald shouldn't put you at ease.
583.sl_trans: In dejstvo, da vaš oče ni plešast, vas ne sme pomiriti.

584.sl_source: Si se odločila, kaj boš počela svoj zadnji dan?
584.en_source: Have you decided what you're going to do on your last day?
584.sl_trans: Ste se že odločili, kaj boste počeli zadnji dan?

587.sl_source: Torej, danes je vaš zadnji dan.
587.en_source: So today is your last day.
587.sl_trans: Danes je torej vaš zadnji dan.

588.sl_source: Kot je običaj, lahko izberete, kako želite preživeti zadnjo noč.
588.en_source: And as is customary, you can choose how you would like to spend your last night.
588.sl_trans: In kot je v navadi, lahko izberete, kako želite preživeti zadnjo noč.

589.sl_source: Smiselno bi bilo izbrati nekaj, česar ne morete početi kot žival.
589.en_source: What I always say in these situations is, it would be wise to choose something you can't do as an animal.
589.sl_trans: Vedno rečem, da bi bilo pametno izbrati nekaj, česar kot žival ne moreš početi.
